Hello to the library application,

Here's the packages requirement to make sure that the application will be STABLE.

OS : 	debian 11

Java :
		openjdk-17-jdk
		penjdk-17-jre

IDE : 	Eclipse
		Version: 2021-06 (4.20.0)
		Build id: 20210612-2011
	
DB : 	libmariadb-java
		mariadb-client
		mariadb-server
		odbc-mariadb
		
Now the Database requirement :
In the folder Script :
		Source or copy/paste the content of the file 01-create-user.sql in mysql
		Source or copy/paste the content of the file 02_biblio_db_creating_script.sql in mysql
		
Database created now time to fill the data into the table :
		Run as Java application the Java class located in the package biblio_server.hibernate.fill_table (AddData.java)

Data added to the Database, good job.
